171
00:11:34,060 --> 00:11:37,029
I mean, I see bad, bad things.

172
00:11:37,196 --> 00:11:40,165
And my job is to find who is at fault...

173
00:11:40,332 --> 00:11:41,822
...and hold them into account.

174
