because I'm not cheap.

209
00:14:00,973 --> 00:14:03,806
So long as you're a better lawyer
than a golfer.

210
00:14:06,445 --> 00:14:08,640
I know you're the best.

211
00:14:08,814 --> 00:14:12,079
Which is why I'm gonna pay you
whatever it takes to win.

212
00:14:12,251 --> 00:14:13,377
Now we're talking.

213
00:14:13,552 --> 00:14:14,678
Have you read the will?

214
00:14:17,590 --> 00:14:19,854
Have I read the will?

215
00:14:21,393 --> 00:14:22,883
You know that sister of yours?

216
00:14:23,062 --> 00:14:25,496
She didn't do you any favors, did she?

217
00:14:25,898 --> 00:14:28,128
I don't care what she told you.

218
00:14:28,901 --> 00:14:32,928
All right, look, your father's will is not
gonna be an issue, okay? It's cut-and-dry.

219
00:14:33,105 --> 00:14:36,905
