for your sister, none to you.

220
00:14:37,209 --> 00:14:40,542
Should she die before the age of 40,
you become the sole heir.

221
00:14:41,046 --> 00:14:44,243
Perfect. She's 39.

222
00:14:45,851 --> 00:14:49,651
Right, but she's not dead, Lance.

223
00:14:52,024 --> 00:14:54,117
