What more do they want?

226
00:15:01,066 --> 00:15:02,499
What more do they want?

227
00:15:02,668 --> 00:15:03,862
Did you just ask me that?

228
00:15:04,169 --> 00:15:06,899
They want a body,
that's what they want.

229
00:15:07,139 --> 00:15:09,972
This is Angelica Vita
we're talking about here.

230
00:15:10,142 --> 00:15:14,511
Her disappearance is the biggest
vanishing act since, what, Howard Hughes?

231
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:16,910
People are gonna want some answers.

232
00:15:17,082 --> 00:15:19,642
And after one look at that will...

233
00:15:20,853 --> 00:15:23,378
...you are gonna be suspect number one,
my friend.

234
00:15:23,555 --> 00:15:24,886
[SELANI GRUNTS]

235
00:15:25,658 --> 00:15:27,387
Yeah, that's not good.

236
00:15:41,907 --> 00:15:43,465
Good afternoon.

237
00:15:43,642 --> 00:15:45,837
Jake Russell,
Los Angeles Police Department.

238
00:15:52,584 --> 00:15:54,814
EVERETT:
You've got 90 seconds. Don't sit.

239
00:15:54,987 --> 00:15:57,217
You're wasting time.
Down to 83 seconds.

240
00:15:57,389 --> 00:16:00,153
Angelica Vita went missing
and hasn't been heard from since.

241
00:16:00,326 --> 00:16:02,294
I have a TV.
Tell me what I don't know.

242
00:16:02,461 --> 00:16:06,864
Two weeks prior to her disappearance,
she made phone calls to a Dr. Richard Ortus.

243
00:16:07,032 --> 00:16:10,058
She had cancer.
People with cancer call doctors.

244
00:16:11,637 --> 00:16:14,663
Dr. Ortus is not an oncologist.

245
00:16:15,107 --> 00:16:17,234
He's a cryogenics expert.

246
00:16:17,543 --> 00:16:21,639
Two days before he arrived, she filed
10 different trusts in the Cook Islands.

247
00:16:21,814 --> 00:16:27,252
All funded with exactly the same amount
of money, $24.2 million.

248
00:16:27,419 --> 00:16:30,513
Contents are sealed, but we know
they have the same executor.

249
00:16:30,689 --> 00:16:34,455
Petros Dimitrios. He's a Greek national,
long-time confidante.

250
00:16:34,626 --> 00:16:38,118
Dimitrios personally runs seven
of her largest companies.

251
00:16:38,297 --> 00:16:40,424
Namely in tourism, hotels and shipping.

252
00:16:40,833 --> 00:16:46,032
Three days after her disappearance,
one of these trusts transferred $1 million...

253
00:16:46,205 --> 00:16:49,038
...to a company in Switzerland
known as Endless Horizon.

254
